body:
Changing the `webpack` key in `karma.conf.js` to this enables sourcemaps for all test runs, which changes the traceback to include the correct line (but not column) for errors:

``` js
webpack: Object.assign(WEBPACK_CONFIG[0], {
  devtool: 'inline-source-map',
}),
```

